	<div class="small-12 main_content columns">
					<article id="post-12" class="post-12 page type-page status-publish hentry">
				<header class="entry-header">
					
					<h1 class="entry-title">Candidates</h1>
				</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
					<div class="row">
<div class="small-2 columns">
<dl class="tabs vertical" data-tab="">
<dd class="active"><a href="#panel1">About</a></dd>
<dd><a href="#panel2">Industries &#038; Positions</a></dd>
<dd><a href="#panel3">Employee Benefits</a></dd>
<dd><a href="#panel4">How to Apply</a></dd>
</dl>
<dl class="tabs vertical">
<dd><a href="http://search3.smartsearchonline.com/tplusinc/jobs_build/process_jobsearch.asp" target="_blank">Job Board</a></dd>
</dl></div>
<div class="small-10 columns">
<div class="tabs-content">
<div id="panel1" class="content active">
<div class="row">
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns" style="padding-left:40px;">
<h5>When it comes to employees, our relationships stand the test of time</h5>
<p>						With 30 years of staffing experience, Technology Plus understands the importance of building great relationships with our work force. For this reason, our approach is firmly grounded in fairness and honesty. We believe candidates should have a realistic view of the position and its potential duration so they can make sound decisions about each assignment. Additionally, our staff is attentive and responsive to the needs of our employees, providing support and helping each employee succeed.</p>
<p>						It is our intent to match candidates with client requirements utilizing the individual’s talents and expertise. Doing so strengthens our relationships with both our employees and our clientele, creating a win-win situation.
					</p></div>
<div class="medium-4 hide-for-small columns">
<div class="cut-image">
						<img src="http://tplusinc.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/techplus/foundation/img/Candidates.gif" />
</div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div id="panel2" class="content">
<div class="row">
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns" style="padding-left:40px;">
<h5>Common Industries and Positions</h5>
<p>						While Technology Plus has deep roots in the refinery and petrochemical industries, we commonly provide personnel for a broad spectrum of industries, including:</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Architectural</li>
<li>Construction </li>
<li>Chemical</li>
<li>Civil/Structural</li>
<li>Facilities</li>
<li>Agricultural</li>
<li>Alternative Fuels &#038; Energy</li>
</ul></div>
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Pharmaceutical</li>
<li>Power</li>
<li>Refinery</li>
<li>Telecommunications</li>
<li>Heavy Industrial</li>
<li>Waste Treatment</li>
<li>Manufacturing</li>
</ul></div>
</p></div>
<p>						Within these industries, Technology Plus personnel encompass a variety of disciplines, including:</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Engineers</li>
<li>Designers </li>
<li>CAD Operators</li>
<li>Field Personnel</li>
<li>Project Managers</li>
</ul></div>
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Estimators</li>
<li>Expeditors</li>
<li>Project Engineers</li>
<li>Schedulers</li>
</ul></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div class="medium-4 hide-for-small columns">
<div class="cut-image">
						<img src="http://tplusinc.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/techplus/foundation/img/Candidates.gif" />
</div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div id="panel3" class="content">
<div class="row">
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns" style="padding-left:40px;">
<h5>Technology Plus Benefits</h5>
<p>						As a Technology Plus employee, you will enjoy a competitive benefits package that includes:</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Group Medical</li>
<li>GAP/Medical Bridge Insurance</li>
<li>Dental/Vision Coverage</li>
<li>Life Insurance</li>
</ul></div>
<div class="small-6 columns">
<ul>
<li>Short- &amp; Long-term Disability Coverage</li>
<li>401(k) Plan</li>
<li>Payroll Direct Deposit </li>
</ul></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div class="medium-4 hide-for-small columns">
<div class="cut-image">
						<img src="http://tplusinc.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/techplus/foundation/img/Candidates.gif" />
</div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div id="panel4" class="content">
<div class="row">
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns" style="padding-left:40px;">
<h5>Interested in pursuing a position?</h5>
<p>						Technology Plus is constantly seeking out new candidates, and we regularly update our <a href="http://search3.smartsearchonline.com/tplusinc/jobs/process_jobsearch.asp">Job Board</a> with new requirements. Simply <a href="http://search3.smartsearchonline.com/tplusinc/jobs/membership.asp">Create an Account</a> to be added to our list of potential candidates. Once your resume has been reviewed, you will be contacted as positions matching your talents become available. You may also monitor our job board regularly and apply for positions yourself.</p></div>
<div class="medium-4 hide-for-small columns">
<div class="cut-image">
						<img src="http://tplusinc.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/techplus/foundation/img/Candidates.gif" />
</div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</div>
